t4:

i’m no artist, but isn’t it better to start with an overall working of the model then focus on details?

matters what you are doing or preferences really. I prefer modeling a low poly mesh and subdivided to make it higher poly. the opposite way is to model a high poly and add as a normal map/bump map on the low poly.
